create instance , generate key , select Amazon linux , add security grp as http and sourse code as 0.0.0.0/0 . then launch -> connect -> copy public ip

sudo yum update -y
sudo yum install httpd -y
sudo systemctl start httpd
sudo systemctl enable httpd
sudo systemctl status httpd

sudo nano /var/www/html/index.html

 HTML CODE -> CTRL O -> ENTER -> CTRL X -> REFERESH IP
